you know?

292
00:11:19.046 --> 00:11:20.914
Storming off into the night.

293
00:11:21.014 --> 00:11:22.482
slamming doors...
that kind of stuff.

294
00:11:22.582 --> 00:11:24.317
- That's so cool.
- I-I just think we got together

295
00:11:24.417 --> 00:11:27.120
