I'm gonna be a witness for them.

348
00:14:05.946 --> 00:14:07.347
Against Tyler.

349
00:14:07.447 --> 00:14:09.249
I figure it's my civic duty
to let the community know

350
00:14:09.382 --> 00:14:12.052
